<h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">About this site</h1>

<p >This site provides a browseable catalogue of AI tools being used in the public sector using public data scraped from the web and provided by the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/government-digital-service">Government Digital Service (GDS)</a> in their <a href="https://cddo-af.data.gov.uk/other/public_access/ai_tools_catalogue/AI-tools-catalogue-pilot.html" target="_blank" class="govuk-link">AI Tools Knowledge Graph</a>.</p>

<p>It was built by <a href="https://www.peterkappus.com/?utm_source=aitools" class="govuk-link">Peter Kappus</a> using <a href="https://www.11ty.dev/" class="govuk-link" target="_blank">11ty</a> and the <a href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/" class="govuk-link" target="_blank">GOV.UK Design System</a> and a little help from <a href="https://cursor.com/">Cursor</a>.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m" id="disclaimer">DISCLAIMER</h2>

<p>This site was developed independently and is not in any way affiliated with or endorsed by GDS, DSIT, or any other government entity.</p>


<p>This site is provided AS-IS with no warranty or guarantee of any kind. Data may not be 100% accurate and should always be verified by visiting the source URL for any tool.</p>

<p>In no event shall Peter Kappus, PNK Industries Limited, or anyone else be held responsible for any losses suffered as a result of using this site. Use at your own risk. 😀</p>

<p >Please direct all queries to <a href="https://www.peterkappus.com/contact">Peter Kappus</a>.</p>

